data.description: Please see this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the heart of Yuma. It is conveniently located near schools, shopping centers, and offers easy access to I-8 and MCAS. This lovely home boasts over 1100 sq ft of living space, with beautiful laminate flooring in the living area, a breakfast bar in the kitchen, and easy-care landscaping. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity!
